data.description: This beautiful single story property sits on a quarter acre lots and features a 3 car garage, over sized side shed for extra storage, RV parking and lots more! Enjoy endless hot water throughout the home  with the newly installed Rheem tankless water heater or relax outside with breath taking views of the franklin mountains from both the front and backyard of the home for sunrise or sunset. Schedule your showing today!
